{"type":"answer","id":3050,"parentType":"question","parentId":691,"uid":902,"contents":"我就从用户体验方面答一波：<br>\n<br>\n手机网页端完全报废，每次点进去都要请求桌面站点。<br>\n<br>\n谁稀罕用你那破APP。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180508/dd430e4da2ff515928f8b6d4810b9801.PNG\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180508/dd430e4da2ff515928f8b6d4810b9801.PNG\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180508/dd430e4da2ff515928f8b6d4810b9801.PNG\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n（首页下滑弹出骚扰框）<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180508/3fb42bf0a4d9a522ab8ad6cdb4aae8c1.JPG\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180508/3fb42bf0a4d9a522ab8ad6cdb4aae8c1.JPG\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180508/3fb42bf0a4d9a522ab8ad6cdb4aae8c1.JPG\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n（点击评论区、查看全部答案强行跳转至推广页）<br>\n<br>\n最后，预祝知乎再次被查封<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180508/dd430e4da2ff515928f8b6d4810b9801.PNG\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180508/dd430e4da2ff515928f8b6d4810b9801.PNG\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180508/dd430e4da2ff515928f8b6d4810b9801.PNG\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180508/3fb42bf0a4d9a522ab8ad6cdb4aae8c1.JPG\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180508/3fb42bf0a4d9a522ab8ad6cdb4aae8c1.JPG\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180508/3fb42bf0a4d9a522ab8ad6cdb4aae8c1.JPG\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-05-08","agreeCount":11,"discussionCount":0}